Dbms
dbms is a software system that mananages, stores and retrives data efficcently 


. reduce data redundancy and inconsistency through centralized control 
. support concurrent data access , transaction management and automate backups 

2/ types of database model 
2.1 hirerchical database model 

concept 
. data organized in tree structure 
. one to many relationship 
. each child has only one parent 

example 
organization structure 


network database model 

. data organise as grapoh 
. support many to many relationship 
. child can have multiple parents

example organization activity 
. telecom network 
. transport system 


relationship database models 
concept 

data stored in tables(relation)
. rows = tuples 
. column = attributes 

example 
MySQL 
Microsoft SQL server 


4. object oriented database model 
concept 

data is stores as object not table 
. database are designed to handle data structure such as multimedia , graphics and large files
. combine database + oop concept 

features 
. objects
. classes
. inheritance 
. encapsulasion 

example . object dB
used in :
. engineering applications
.scientific database 
. multimedia db.

object relationship
concept  
